		{
			dependencies: ["630F7B4B08640585"]
			description: ["The Tinker's Workshop is your crafting foundation. The Tinker Station assembles tools from individually crafted parts; the Part Builder shapes raw materials into heads, handles, and bindings using pattern blanks; the Crafting Station connects to adjacent inventories for streamlined crafting. Build all three and keep them together — they work best as a set."]
