		{
			dependencies: ["630F7B4B08640585"]
			description: ["A bed sets your respawn point and skips the night, but in this world it also enables placing a Waystone. Waystones are teleportation anchors — place one at your base and activate others found in villages and structures across the continent. Fast travel becomes essential once your operations span multiple biomes."]
