		}
		{
			dependencies: ["78CD039E8C931F77"]
			description: ["Copper is found at mid-depths in quantity. Smelt it into ingots for early crafting and as a component in Create's Andesite Alloy. The Blast Furnace reward gives you a head start on smelting efficiency — place it early and use it to process copper, iron, and gold faster than a standard furnace."]
