		{
			dependencies: ["78CD039E8C931F77"]
			description: ["Spirit Iron Ore generates at iron depth and glows faintly blue-grey. Smelt it into Spirit Iron Ingots — the base material for all early Soul Land crafting, including the Forging Table and Spirit Iron armor. It also gates access to this pack's custom Nature's Compass recipe, modified to require Spirit Iron."]
