		{
			dependencies: ["5E33BC8AED91B4B9"]
			description: ["The Silent Sleeve Dart is the entry point of the Tang Sect's hidden weapon system — compact needles fired in rapid bursts from concealed wrist-mounted launchers. It requires minimal soul power to operate and can be used effectively from rank 1. Upgrade to higher-tier Tang Sect weapons as your cultivation advances."]
