			description: ["The Flying God Claw is a mid-tier Tang Sect hidden weapon — a retractable steel claw launched on a wire, capable of grappling targets, pulling items, and striking at range. It demands more soul power than the Sleeve Dart but delivers far greater versatility in combat."]
