			description: ["Mine & Slash uses a gear soul system to modify your equipment. Weapon stat souls are applied to weapons to set a primary damage stat — physical, elemental, or soul power scaling. Your first Common soul is the baseline; upgrade to higher rarity souls as you find them to dramatically increase your damage output."]
