			description: ["The Armor stat soul family specializes in raw physical defense — increased armor rating, damage reduction, and physical resistance. This is the path for frontline fighters who intend to stand toe-to-toe with spirit beasts. Stack armor souls across all four pieces for maximum protection before entering the Star Dou Forest."]
