			dependencies: ["1743DDFA6AFDF584"]
			description: ["The Smeltery enables your first real ore processing chain. Ores placed inside melt directly into liquid metal, and most ore types yield 1.5x the metal output compared to direct smelting. This is the foundation of the ore processing chapter — the next step is Create's Crushing Wheels for full doubling."]
