			description: ["Mine & Slash's armor system gives you three defensive identity paths — raw mitigation, evasion, and magic barrier. Each piece of armor can be specialized independently, but a consistent path across all four slots is more effective than mixing. Revisit this choice when you reach Manasteel and Spirit Steel armor tiers; the path that works now may not be optimal later."]
